1.install pandas in the centos

yum install zeromq-devel  
yum install gcc-gfortran  
yum install freetype-devel  
yum install libpng-devel  
yum install atlas-devel  
yum install bzip2-devel  
yum install tk-devel  
yum install tcl-devel 
yum -y install blas blas-devel lapack-devel lapack
yum -y install seaborn scipy
yum -y install freetype freetype-devel libpng libpng-devel
yum install gcc-c++


yum -y install python-pip
pip install -U setuptools
pip install cython
pip uninstall numpy
pip install numpy==1.7.0
pip install pandas==0.16.2

2. check python package info 

先用命令pip freeze查看已经安装的package及版本.
如果安装了ansible,就执行命令pip uninstall ansible卸载之.
最后运行命令pip install ansible==1.9.6安装我们要的版本.
